# link-zulip Foundation

LiNKtrend fork of **Zulip** server and web app—large Python/Django + TypeScript codebase with many submodules and tooling paths per upstream.

## Conventions

- Follow Zulip’s documented dev setup (Vagrant, tools, linters) for non-trivial changes.
- Internal comms product for LiNKtrend—keep fork-only patches clearly separated for upstream sync.
